- Why would it be goodto be unlike you?

34:20.335 --> 34:23.168
- Right. Sorry.

34:23.210 --> 34:26.295
- Listen, why don't you ordera pizza? If we start now,

34:26.295 --> 34:28.629
we could be finishedall this by 11.

