- You know what? I forgot.I have my group tonight.

34:34.545 --> 34:36.670
- Tonight?- Yeah.

34:36.670 --> 34:40.005
I hope you're notterribly disappointed.

34:40.045 --> 34:42.547
- So, so it's going well, then?

34:42.630 --> 34:45.047
- It's a process.

34:45.089 --> 34:48.005
- Wow. You know, I am so gladthat you are getting --

34:48.089 --> 34:51.382
whoa -- what you need from it.- I am.

34:51.422 --> 34:53.965
- Well, OK.(Edward chuckles.)

34:59.341 --> 35:01.216
- Sorry I'm late.Oh! Is it over?

35:01.258 --> 35:04.591
- We're going on a field trip.- Well, this is a nice surprise.

35:04.633 --> 35:06.216
- I think I was in conflict.

