- Now, the objectiveof this exercise

35:43.096 --> 35:46.096
is to stall in the lineas long as you can.

35:46.138 --> 35:49.805
So I want you to feel the heatof the conflict rising

35:49.847 --> 35:52.805
around you, because you'reholding up the line. Got it?

35:52.805 --> 35:55.722
(beep)Go.

35:57.140 --> 35:59.473
- What does it say? Do I evenwanna know what it says?

