"Partner two: escalate thesituation by becoming agitated

36:08.932 --> 36:10.974
and claim to be in a rush."I'll take that one. Easy.

36:10.974 --> 36:13.767
- Cinco Dublin just got chosenfor the losing team.

36:13.808 --> 36:16.225
- I don't think so. I never losewhen there's a prize at stake.

36:16.267 --> 36:20.559
- There's a firsttime for everything.- No, I don't think so.

36:25.143 --> 36:27.559
- $8 and 30 cents.

36:27.601 --> 36:30.602
- Lea Townshend, is that you?

36:30.644 --> 36:34.102
- Wow, Mrs. Musgrave.What are you doing back in town?

36:34.144 --> 36:37.936
- Well, we moved back. Didn'tyour mother tell you?- No.

36:37.978 --> 36:40.436
- I hear your novelis doing great.

36:40.478 --> 36:42.478
- OK, let's not writea novel right now

36:42.478 --> 36:44.145
and keep things moving,shall we?

36:44.145 --> 36:47.104
- You're not listening. One ofus has to go get another item

36:47.146 --> 36:49.187
to hold up the line!- You always do this!

36:49.229 --> 36:51.354
I just said I would goand get some spinach.

36:51.396 --> 36:53.730
- (barely audible): May I havea price check on that?

36:53.772 --> 36:56.938
- (whispering): Louder.She can't hear you.

36:56.980 --> 36:59.313
- (whispering): May I havea price check on that?

36:59.313 --> 37:01.313
- Carol. You can do it.

37:01.313 --> 37:05.231
- It was very nice to see you.- Oh, maybe we can doa ladies' brunch.

37:05.273 --> 37:09.481
- That would be perfect.- That's wonderful. Let's pullout our calendars and set a date

37:09.481 --> 37:13.565
for brunch rightnow. Yeah. Yeah?

