- Well, wheneverEdward's name comes up,

46:19.340 --> 46:22.091
you get a little agitated,so I'm thinking

46:22.132 --> 46:25.424
maybe there's something you'renot dealing with with Edward,

46:25.466 --> 46:28.549
your second cousin?- No. As I've said before,

46:28.591 --> 46:32.800
and often, I don't have anyproblems with Edward.

