- Yeah, that side of the familyhas amazing recuperative skills.

46:42.551 --> 46:45.343
- Ah, wow. How about your side?

46:47.177 --> 46:49.177
- You know, I didn'twant to say anything,

46:49.219 --> 46:51.844
but I haven't been feeling sogreat the last few minutes.

46:51.885 --> 46:55.136
So I think I should probably go.

46:55.178 --> 46:57.761
- Can I give you a ride home?- No, I have a car.

46:57.803 --> 47:00.928
- Is there really an Edward?

