- That's very sweet,but not very accurate.

47:20.598 --> 47:22.556
(chair clattering)

47:22.556 --> 47:25.764
(quietly): Excuse me.

47:46.017 --> 47:50.017
- (Cinco):And I just need someone to explain it to me --

47:50.059 --> 47:51.934
this Venus versus Mars equation.

47:51.976 --> 47:55.227
I am so tired of trying to crack that code.

47:55.268 --> 47:57.893
I'm at lunch with a very attractive,

